data.title: What does Iran think about Sultan Selim who beat Shah Ismail?
data.meta_description:
Answer (1 of 2): People don't care about this matter if they even know about that in the first place.

Of course, they do care about historical events like Arab's conquer. But this case is a little bit different. we didn't lose many or we took them back during the other Safavid Kings.
